---
import Container from "../../components/container.astro";
import CTA from "@components/CTA.astro";
import Features from "../../components/features.astro";
import Hero from "../../components/hero.astro";
import Logos from "../../components/logos.astro";
import Navbar from "../../components/navbar/navbar.astro";
import Reviews from "../../components/reviews.astro";
import Contactbtn from "../../components/contactbtn.astro";
import Btn from "../../components/btn.astro";
import LogoBrands from "../../components/js/logo-brands.astro";
import Areas from "../../components/areas.astro";
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";

import "css/service/style_services.css";
import "css/style-index.css";
---
  <Layout title="OSHA Certified Appliance Repair | Safe Service" description="Get OSHA-certified appliance repair for safe, reliable service. Our expert technicians ensure compliance and top-quality repairs. Call (323) 870-4790">
  <Navbar />
<Reviews />
    <div style="margin:0 40px 0 40px;">
    <h1>OSHA Certified Appliance Repair | Safe & Professional Service</h1>
    <div class="image-text-container">
        <figure class="image-wrapper">
          <img
            src="/credentials/osha-certified-appliance-repair-company.jpg"
            loading="lazy"
            alt="Osha Certified Appliance Repair Company"
            width="500"
            height="500"
          />
          <figcaption>Osha Certified Appliance Repair Company</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <div class="text-content">
            <section>
                <h2>✔Trusted OSHA Certified Technicians for Safe Appliance Repairs</h2>
                <p>When it comes to appliance repair, safety is a top priority. At <strong>Same Day Appliance Repair</strong>, we employ <strong>OSHA-certified technicians</strong> who follow strict **safety standards and compliance protocols** to ensure safe, professional, and efficient appliance repairs.</p>
            </section>
            <section>
                <h2>✅ Why Choose Our OSHA Certified Appliance Repair Services?</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li> <strong>Certified for Workplace & Home Safety</strong> – Our technicians are trained in **OSHA safety protocols**, ensuring safe appliance handling.</li>
                    <li> <strong>Same-Day Service</strong> – We provide **fast and reliable appliance repairs** to minimize downtime.</li>
                    <li> <strong>Expert Repairs for All Major Brands</strong> – We fix appliances from leading brands like **Samsung, LG, Whirlpool, GE, Bosch & more**.</li>
                    <li> <strong>Compliance with OSHA Standards</strong> – Ensuring **safety in every repair**, protecting both technicians and customers.</li>
                    <li> <strong>Upfront Pricing & Warranty-Backed Repairs</strong> – No surprises! We offer **transparent pricing** with a **service warranty**.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>
     </div>
     <section>
        <h2> What is OSHA Certification?</h2>
        <p>**OSHA (Occupational Safety and Health Administration) certification** ensures that technicians are trained in **workplace safety, hazard prevention, and proper handling of appliances and tools**. At <strong>Same Day Appliance Repair</strong>, our **OSHA-certified technicians** adhere to these standards to provide **safe and efficient appliance repairs**.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>🔍 Appliances We Repair with OSHA Certified Expertise</h2>
        <ul>
            <li> <strong>Refrigerators & Freezers</strong> – Fixing **compressor issues, refrigerant leaks, and cooling failures**.</li>
            <li> <strong>Washers & Dryers</strong> – Repairing **drainage problems, noisy operation, and heating malfunctions**.</li>
            <li> <strong>Ovens & Stoves</strong> – Addressing **burner malfunctions, temperature inconsistencies, and gas leaks**.</li>
            <li> <strong>Dishwashers</strong> – Fixing **leaks, drainage problems, and faulty wash cycles**.</li>
            <li> <strong>Commercial & Industrial Appliances</strong> – Repairing **walk-in freezers, commercial ovens, and industrial dishwashers**.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>With our **OSHA-certified technicians**, you can rest assured that your appliance is repaired with **safety, compliance, and efficiency in mind**.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2> The Benefits of Hiring an OSHA Certified Technician</h2>
        <ul>
            <li> <strong>Compliance with Workplace & Home Safety Regulations</strong> – Protecting both customers and technicians.</li>
            <li>🛠 <strong>Proper Handling of Appliances & Tools</strong> – Reducing risks of damage and ensuring long-lasting repairs.</li>
            <li>⚠ <strong>Injury Prevention & Hazard Reduction</strong> – Technicians follow safety protocols to prevent accidents.</li>
            <li> <strong>Peace of Mind</strong> – Knowing your appliance is in the hands of a **certified safety expert**.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>📞 Schedule a Repair with Our OSHA Certified Technicians Today!</h2>
        <p>Don't take risks with unqualified repairs! Contact <strong>Same Day Appliance Repair</strong> for **safe, professional, and OSHA-compliant appliance repair services**.</p>
    </section>
    <Btn />
    </div>
<CTA phone="(323) 870-4790" branch="West Hollywood" zones={["Los Angeles", "Southern California"]} />
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "HomeAndConstructionBusiness",
  "name": "Same Day Appliance Repair",
  "telephone": "(323) 870-4790",
  "url": "https://samedayappliance.repair",
  "priceRange": "$",
  "hasCredential": {
    "@type": "EducationalOccupationalCredential",
    "credentialCategory": "certification",
    "name": "OSHA Safety Certification",
    "recognizedBy": {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "Occupational Safety and Health Administration (OSHA)",
      "url": "https://www.osha.gov"
    }
  },
  "description": "Get OSHA-certified appliance repair for safe, reliable service. Our expert technicians ensure compliance and top-quality repairs. Call (323) 870-4790",
  "mainEntityOfPage": "https://samedayappliance.repair/credentials/osha-certified-appliance-repair/"
}
</script>
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
